[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering dependencies and testing**\n\nI need to build the dependencies for JUnit 5 and AssertJ, and I could add a test while I'm at it. I've got to make sure I understand XML Catalog references. There’s also the DataType with setRefId — maybe I should look into using Reference there. It's a bit puzzling, but I'm eager to read more about DataType to clarify everything. Let's untangle this!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_001a31f5e364dad30169f58f1c9a8c8192a1db708da9fe1df9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9Y8eJL1NPnjlBKWKkCMmm2VCotnMtUAh-jbJzQC19LzDHg5ZwGwQBJ3vpr9u6GIF4aLkpIuKRBl3HgHYzpn2Do4iKGsN4UvoppREdwwsFHeoxvrlDJ64jI1guX_bzo7R1EhVeqg8gaKK8H3iDbV31FpWhgqmiAsUOwcnws6LQzeS_eLrPx73DvNtck1nm_bike2pYSpFrYROlZ-8f-cskiUJPFksW8jRgsPjt3aPr7hzi4a8Gl4MRJbEcURHj19ohRnIFE03VOZjHdivg6Ex8jwoaZafJi3vNrm1EE5mwIwvi-W1cJVDBEAGyyEsRe-DRNpBVtjWKscWzUrAJnC1OaS3Mat9_nkt41iulZKtQEpJmZp_cGFJisGoj3SXZv8e02Q_X79r4wbh3ofy-IFxL_qt53vc7igxtuZAcCRzy_Okt84Mmya07FMrCnDjqxDvKl3i-XjS5vRr7S4Aj_OlZAzMxnohixaiVg6N5oziccDzk2hO_iH5oaGajIJxRSgcH6bzxhcsvxnp3w55exZ6BK6ieIONfD6B9RKoCMakTcKyDZ6SoSNWQUKnyeti0iI3dUQ2N9MdRRjMO6wmPU4g1Q3FwPtvDuOWx8oTSD-0zqnt-zvCNRIgqeulRl6voJo7sFVm2rm7H9m0UJhspl9wIg2PdTc-wBsdN8Eh9pKd9QZUuwiVozSeDGmyCR9ALh-sbWz0ebrSXO7_25Kqr6FT1BqD0RVlJv65HWkEejDT2dweK80pTxbnf4A81OkbWB0fCAW-22VatPAScd2WGf1bYEcUBOdrKN5ERXE_wg9CBVdm5KbZ-EiOySIky79yVBUfkWMtuewsfiakro8XGIa3vAshUVk3n-p1ScFTfoVD-wBun-AtO5X48JmgFDL38BJb6eIcS0nRpZ6DL0ZpPLMNXXa2qaW8G8w6_yWbyJoBZtjDm7b8Vkch_-QF9YgSOJc14wIvat4b1yf0r_I50zAroJhaB62qEIIV2pVY5VIaWKBY4aRMCEhVuDBXasffDSfVugS9dKBO0OzTPbETcE7vxe87Mni46_25S2CbeFilbarro7TagL9MLyA8ouFoQUrK9syZ5f4FarKURdtWWzkpWxVtpMsSAjAYbyO6tjYSOQz-mHo=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering dependencies and testing**\\n\\nI need to build the dependencies for JUnit 5 and AssertJ, and I could add a test while I'm at it. I've got to make